Time":"2020-01-08T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚多狗屈一個人，證供都唔夾下，唔撚好以為警察就一定岩一定告到人先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d8be29744686e6552b342d0b7092cc2c0d389e","tid":1816802,"uid":65760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cbd35b4212009bbe01ddc7f52473bbab8e6dd83","tid":1816802,"uid":70336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"証人咁多唔記得 唔確定<br />\n點告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"裁判官: 基於警察係誠實可靠嘅証人，雖然佢話唔記得，但我相信佢話有就有&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0154b872c36d106911d5e0eaacf20711e20b64ce","tid":1816802,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"疑點利益 打甩"},{"pid":"6568261d5fe5b9c6c2402952a79bd1fb0e9f8ce6","tid":1816802,"uid":156579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"求其你出現左就入得<br />\n轉左轉埋右轉幾個圈又有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87201472346094f785537730e2f7439c4330f5a8","tid":1816802,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"誠實證人呀狗官"}]}